{"title":"各族人民永远跟党走","authors":["牟本理"],"dates":[{"year":2002,"month":11,"day":3}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"各族人民永远跟党走"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牟本理"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在历史前进的重要时刻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在硕果丰盈的收获季节，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从经济腾飞的沿海，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到万里边疆的村落，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"各族儿女喜迎十六大，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"同声赞颂伟大的党，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纵情歌唱亲爱的祖国。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一路春风，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"岁月如歌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"各族儿女心中永远高唱："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有共产党就没有新中国。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最难忘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"南湖的航船，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"井冈的星火，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"遵义的历史抉择，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长征的坎坷曲折，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宝塔山红灯闪闪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天安门彩旗猎猎。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"各族人民站了起来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迎来一个崭新的世界。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春风浩荡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吹遍中国，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们走进了改革开放的岁月。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最难忘："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"真理标准的讨论，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三中全会的号角，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"深圳特区的奇迹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上海浦东的伟业，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"港澳回归，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“神舟”奔月，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"加入世贸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"申奥喜悦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"发展经济，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"创新开拓，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国速度，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"气壮山河。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全世界注视着，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"东方崛起一个强大的中国。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"西部大开发展开了新的征程，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"民族地区翻开了新的一页。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"青藏铁路唤醒了沉睡的高原，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"南水北调滋润着每一片荒漠，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金光大道把边疆和北京紧紧相连，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"村村通电点亮了万家灯火。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"退耕还林，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"重整山河。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"兴边富民，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扶贫济弱。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"共同进步，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日子红火。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五十六个民族心连心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"道路越走越宽阔。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊，这一切的一切都告诉我："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只有共产党才能发展中国。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民幸福，党在领路，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中华复兴，党在掌舵。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“三个代表”的思想，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"已经印入各族人民的心窝。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跳吧！跳起欢乐的锅庄。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唱吧！唱起醉人的酒歌。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"各族人民永远跟党走，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"共同建设富强的中国。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}